name: Ambigrammatic Figure #0175 (Card 46/55)
description: Created by Golan Levin (@golan) and Lingdong Huang (@LingdongH) with a machine learning system, this is #46 of 55 works in the Ambigrammatic Figure Series (2020). The grotesque face in this loop is an "ambigram": an image that is legible both upside-down and right-side-up.
